snippet: Rookie forward Kristaps Porzingis poured in 26 points to lead the New York Knicks to a gritty 120-114 win over the Boston Celtics Tuesday at Madison Square Garden....
lead_paragraph: Rookie forward Kristaps Porzingis poured in 26 points to lead the New York Knicks to a gritty 120-114 win over the Boston Celtics Tuesday at Madison Square Garden.

headline.main: Porzingis Drives Knicks to Gritty Win Over Celtics
headline.print_headline: Porzingis Drives Knicks to Gritty Win Over Celtics
